Question: Zhejiang Aike Intelligent technology co.,ltd CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Zhejiang Aike Intelligent Technology Co., Ltd

Product: CES 2024 Highlight

- AI-powered terminal devices for hand washing, drying, and disinfection
- Products include tap hand dryers, compact jet hand dryers, brushless motor jet hand dryers, tabletop auto soap dispensers, stainless steel hand dryers, and stainless steel auto soap dispensers
- Production capacity of up to 400,000 pcs hand dryers and 1 million pcs soap dispensers per year
- Owns more than 150 core patented technologies
- Approved by CE, CB, UKCA, UL, GS, CCC, SAA, GCC, PSE, FCC, RoHS, REACH, WEEE, and ERP
- Offers OEM, specialized, standardized, and international production line, and AIKE brand
- Focuses on hand hygiene, cleaning industry, and early-stage small businesses
